cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with scene flow estimation from 3D point clouds. The use of deep neural networks also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The fact that the model is designed to operate on large-scale point clouds suggests that it could also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Finally, the use of lattice points and the restoration of structural information suggests that it could belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
